text: Sanchai and Sonchat Ratiwatana were the defending champions but lost in the semifinals to Hsieh Cheng-peng and Yang Tsung-hua. Hsieh and Yang won the title after defeating Hsu Yu-hsiou and Jimmy Wang 6–7(3–7), 6–2, [10–8] in the final. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ==References== * Main Draw OEC Kaohsiung - Doubles 2018 Doubles
